OL,3,CDoctor raised concerns about Ian
OL,4,CPaterson seven years before his
OL,5,Csuspension
OL,7,FAn NHS doctor who tried to stop the
OL,8,Frogue breast surgeon Ian Paterson has
OL,9,Fdescribed how he raised concerns about
OL,10,Fthe safety of his patients in 2003,
OL,11,Fmore than seven years before Paterson
OL,12,Fwas finally suspended.
OL,14,FInquest hearings into the deaths of 62
OL,15,Fwomen, who died of breast cancer, have
OL,16,Fheard evidence from a former colleague
OL,17,Fof the rogue surgeon Ian Paterson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
