OL,5,Csuspension
OL,7,FHe said the meetings were held to
OL,8,Fdiscuss the treatment plans of up to
OL,9,F40 patients during a weekly, one-hour-
OL,10,Flong meeting.
OL,12,FDr Stockdale told the Coroner: "Mr
OL,13,FPaterson was a forthright individual
OL,14,Fwho held firm views. It was not an
OL,15,Fenvironment for a particularly
OL,16,Fbalanced discussion."
