OL,3,CDoctor raised concerns about Ian
OL,4,CPaterson seven years before his
OL,5,Csuspension
OL,7,FJonathan Jones KC, Counsel to the
OL,8,FInquest, also asked Dr Stockdale about
OL,9,Fevidence he had previously given to
OL,10,Fthe General Medical Council (GMC) and
OL,11,Fthe Ian Kennedy Report (2013).
OL,13,FDr Stockdale said a mastectomy should
OL,14,Fbe a one-time operation but explained
OL,15,Fthat he was seeing patients who had
OL,16,Fmultiple surgeries with Paterson.
OL,18,FHe told the coroner that not removing
OL,19,Fall of the breast tissue gave an
OL,20,Fincreased risk of the cancer returning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
