OL,4,CPaterson seven years before his
OL,5,Csuspension
OL,7,FDr Stockdale told the court: "I am not
OL,8,Fa surgeon. But I recognised that after
OL,9,Fa mastectomy you would expect the
OL,10,Fchest wall would be flat."
OL,12,FHe said he would not have expected any
OL,13,Fmastectomy patients to fit into a bra.
OL,15,FBut it was obvious to him that, for
OL,16,Fsome women, further surgery was
OL,17,Fpossible and therefore he was required
OL,18,Fto refer the patients back to Paterson
OL,19,Ffor further surgery.
