OL,7,FDr Stockdale spoke exclusively to ITV
OL,8,Fin a Tonight Special about the scandal
OL,9,Fin December 2018.
OL,11,FPaterson was jailed in 2017 for
OL,12,Fwounding nine women and one man he
OL,13,Ftreated between 1997 and 2011.
OL,15,FHe convinced them to undergo
OL,16,Foperations by inventing or
OL,17,Fexaggerating the risks of tumours to
OL,18,Fearn extra money and maintain a
OL,19,Fsuccessful reputation.
