OL,3,CDoctor raised concerns about Ian
OL,4,CPaterson seven years before his
OL,5,Csuspension
OL,7,FBishop Graham James, who authored the
OL,8,Finquiry in 2020, said all 11,000
OL,9,Fpatients should be recalled and have
OL,10,Ftheir care reviewed.
OL,12,FInformation was passed from the
OL,13,Finquiry to the coroner, His Honour
OL,14,FRichard Foster, who is now
OL,15,Finvestigating whether there is any
OL,16,Fevidence to suspect that any of the
OL,17,Fformer patients of Paterson died an
OL,18,Funnatural death as a result of his
OL,19,Factions. The first inquests were
OL,20,Fopened in July 2020, with the hearings
OL,21,Fnow resuming in October 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
