OL,7,FOn Monday, the coroner read out the 62
OL,8,Fnames of women at the centre of these
OL,9,Finquests who all died of breast cancer.
OL,11,FHe warned more inquests could still be
OL,12,Fopened.
OL,14,FSo far, 565 deaths have been reviewed
OL,15,F- 20 cases are still outstanding and a
OL,16,Ffurther 15-20 are awaiting further
OL,17,Finvestigations.
