OL,7,FPaterson has had three previous
OL,8,Fapplications for legal aid refused.
OL,9,FPaterson also requested a 28-day
OL,10,Fadjournment which was denied by the
OL,11,Fcoroner.
OL,13,FThe second phase of the inquests will
OL,14,Flook into systemic issues including
OL,15,Fany failings in the recruitment and
OL,16,Fsupervision of Paterson, any systemic
OL,17,Ffailing by the hospital management and
OL,18,Fcorporate governance in addressing
OL,19,Fconcerns raised about Ian Paterson,
OL,20,Fand any failures by the relevant
OL,21,Fregulatory agencies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
