OL,7,FThe coroner will start hearing
OL,8,Fevidence about each patient from next
OL,9,Fweek. The final conclusions from the
OL,10,Fcoroner will be published in 2026.
OL,12,FOn Thursday, Paterson, who is
OL,13,Fcurrently serving a 20-year prison
OL,14,Fsentence, is due to give evidence.
